node.title: Jacinda Ardern going into self-isolation after being deemed close contact of positive case
node.description: The Prime Minister is asymptomatic and is feeling well.
node.content: ["Prime Minister Jacinda Ardern has been deemed a close contact of a positive COVID-19 case, and has entered self-isolation in line with Ministry of Health advice.", "\u00a0", "The exposure event took place on Saturday 22 January during flight NZ8273 from Kerikeri to Auckland. Flight NZ8273 has been added to the Ministry of Health website as a location of interest this evening.", "\u00a0"]
